<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>KYNARIO 2026 — Juicios sobre existir | Kymera Teatro</title>
<meta name="description" content="Un festival de teatro breve de Kymera Teatro. Cinco piezas. Cuatro fechas. Guadalajara, julio 2026.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Libre+Franklin:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --rojo: #8E352E;
    --naranja: #EC6B13;
    --morado: #402942;
    --negro: #000000;
    --blanco: #FFFFFF;
    --gris: #F2EFEA;
    --gris-texto: #6B6860;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Libre Franklin', sans-serif;
    background: var(--negro);
    color: var(--blanco);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* TIPOGRAFÍA DISPLAY */
  .display {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 0.95;
  }

  /* TRIÁNGULO SVG inline */
  .tri {
    display: inline-block;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  /* ─── NAV ─── */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .nav-logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    opacity: 0.9;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-logo:hover { opacity: 1; }

  nav a.cta-nav {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--negro);
    background: var(--naranja);
    padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  nav a.cta-nav:hover { background: #d45e0a; }

  /* ─── HERO ─── */
  #hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--negro);
  }

  .hero-bg-tri {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10%;
    right: -8%;
    width: 65vw;
    max-width: 700px;
    opacity: 0.06;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--naranja);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 14vw, 13rem);
    color: var(--blanco);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.6rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .meta-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .meta-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .meta-value {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--blanco);
  }

  .hero-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  }

  .hero-cta {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  /* ─── BOTONES ─── */
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--negro);
    background: var(--naranja);
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.1s;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover { background: #d45e0a; }
  .btn-primary:active { transform: scale(0.98); }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--blanco);
    background: transparent;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }

  /* ─── SECCIONES ─── */
  section { padding: 5rem 2rem; }

  .section-inner {
    max-width: 1040px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rojo);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    color: var(--blanco);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* ─── SOBRE ─── */
  #sobre {
    background: var(--morado);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--rojo);
  }

  .sobre-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .sobre-text {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .sobre-text p + p { margin-top: 1rem; }

  .quote-block {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--naranja);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .quote-text {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .quote-attr {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
  }

  /* ─── PIEZAS ─── */
  #piezas { background: var(--negro); }

  .piezas-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .pieza-card {
    background: var(--negro);
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .pieza-card:hover { background: #111111; }

  .pieza-num {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 4rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.5rem;
    right: 1rem;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .pieza-titulo {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--blanco);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .pieza-autor {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--naranja);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .pieza-desc {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ─── BOLETOS ─── */
  #boletos { background: #000000; }

  .boletos-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Selector */
  .ticket-box {
    background: #0A0A0A;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .ticket-section-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .fecha-btns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .fecha-btn {
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    padding: 0.75rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'Libre Franklin', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }

  .fecha-btn:hover {
    border-color: var(--naranja);
    color: var(--blanco);
  }

  .fecha-btn.activo {
    background: var(--rojo);
    border-color: var(--rojo);
    color: var(--blanco);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .fecha-btn .dia {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: inherit;
  }

  .fecha-btn.activo .dia { color: var(--blanco); }

  .tipo-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .tipo-info {}
  .tipo-nombre {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--blanco);
  }

  .tipo-precio {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }

  .qty-ctrl {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .qty-btn {
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    color: var(--blanco);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
    font-family: 'Libre Franklin', sans-serif;
  }

  .qty-btn:hover { border-color: var(--naranja); color: var(--naranja); }

  .qty-num {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    min-width: 24px;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--blanco);
  }

  .total-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .total-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  }

  .total-monto {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: var(--blanco);
  }

  #btn-comprar {
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding: 1.1rem;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  /* Panel SPEI */
  .spei-box {
    background: #0A0A0A;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .spei-titulo {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--blanco);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .spei-intro {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .spei-dato {
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .spei-dato-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .spei-dato-val {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--blanco);
    font-family: 'Libre Franklin', sans-serif;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    padding: 0.6rem 0.9rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .spei-dato-val:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }

  .copy-hint {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  }

  .spei-divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .pasos {
    counter-reset: paso;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .pasos li {
    counter-increment: paso;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .pasos li::before {
    content: counter(paso);
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--naranja);
    min-width: 18px;
    margin-top: 0.05rem;
  }

  /* ─── ELENCO ─── */
  #elenco { background: var(--morado); }

  .elenco-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .elenco-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .elenco-avatar {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--naranja);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .elenco-nombre {
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--blanco);
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .elenco-rol {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .elenco-rol span {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    color: var(--naranja);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
  footer {
    background: #000000;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .footer-inner {
    max-width: 1040px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  .footer-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    list-style: none;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .footer-links a {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .footer-links a:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }

  .footer-copy {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* ─── TOAST ─── */
  #toast {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 2rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(4rem);
    background: var(--naranja);
    color: var(--negro);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    pointer-events: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
    z-index: 999;
  }

  #toast.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
  }

  /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    nav { padding: 0.75rem 1rem; }
    section { padding: 3.5rem 1.25rem; }
    .sobre-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .boletos-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    #hero { padding: 7rem 1.25rem 3rem; }
    .hero-bg-tri { width: 90vw; }
    .hero-meta { gap: 1rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Kymera Teatro" style="height:28px;width:auto;"></a>
  <a href="#boletos" class="cta-nav">Boletos</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <svg class="hero-bg-tri" viewBox="0 0 800 750" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:70vw;max-width:760px;top:-5%;right:-10%;">
    <!-- Triángulo grande blanco -->
    <g opacity="0.06">
      <polygon points="400,20 760,700 40,700" stroke="white" stroke-width="3" fill="none"/>
      <polygon points="400,36 742,686 58,686" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
      <polygon points="400,52 724,672 76,672" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none"/>
      <line x1="40" y1="700" x2="760" y2="700" stroke="white" stroke-width="3"/>
      <line x1="30" y1="714" x2="770" y2="714" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.8"/>
    </g>
    <!-- Triángulo naranja -->
    <g opacity="0.09">
      <polygon points="550,80 820,580 280,580" stroke="#EC6B13" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"/>
      <polygon points="550,96 804,568 296,568" stroke="#EC6B13" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
      <polygon points="550,112 788,556 312,556" stroke="#EC6B13" stroke-width="0.8" fill="none"/>
      <line x1="280" y1="580" x2="820" y2="580" stroke="#EC6B13" stroke-width="2.5"/>
      <line x1="270" y1="592" x2="830" y2="592" stroke="#EC6B13" stroke-width="1.2"/>
    </g>
    <!-- Triángulo morado sutil -->
    <g opacity="0.08">
      <polygon points="200,300 480,740 -80,740" stroke="#402942" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
      <polygon points="200,316 464,728 -64,728" stroke="#402942" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
      <line x1="-80" y1="740" x2="480" y2="740" stroke="#402942" stroke-width="2"/>
    </g>
  </svg>

  <p class="hero-eyebrow">Kymera Teatro · Guadalajara · Julio 2026</p>
  <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="KYNARIO 2026 — Juicios sobre existir" style="width:min(780px,92vw);display:block;margin-bottom:2rem;">

  <p style="font-size:clamp(0.85rem,1.8vw,1.1rem);font-weight:300;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:2rem;max-width:520px;line-height:1.7;">Cinco obras originales. Una misma pregunta. Nadie sale siendo exactamente el mismo.</p>

  <div class="hero-meta">
    <div class="meta-item">
      <span class="meta-label">Fechas</span>
      <span class="meta-value">4 · 11 · 18 · 25 de Julio, 2026</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-divider"></div>
    <div class="meta-item">
      <span class="meta-label">Hora</span>
      <span class="meta-value">7:00 PM</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-divider"></div>
    <div class="meta-item">
      <span class="meta-label">Sede</span>
      <span class="meta-value">Punto Escénico, Guadalajara</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-divider"></div>
    <div class="meta-item">
      <span class="meta-label">Preventa</span>
      <span class="meta-value" style="color:var(--naranja)">$250 MXN</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-cta" style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:2rem;">
    <a href="#boletos" class="btn-primary">Comprar boletos →</a>
    <a href="#piezas" class="btn-secondary">Ver el programa</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SOBRE -->
<section id="sobre">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="sobre-grid">
      <div>
        <span class="section-label">¿Qué es KYNARIO?</span>
        <h2 class="display section-title">Un festival de teatro breve sobre existir</h2>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="sobre-text">KYNARIO es un festival de teatro breve creado por Kymera Teatro. Cinco obras originales exploran distintas formas de entender la existencia, la identidad y el vínculo con los demás — desde el absurdo más físico hasta el silencio más incómodo.</p>
        <p class="sobre-text" style="margin-top:1rem;">Cada pieza es autónoma en su universo y su tono, pero todas comparten una misma pregunta de fondo: <strong style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);font-weight:500;">¿quién tiene el derecho de juzgar cómo alguien elige existir?</strong></p>
        <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:2rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <div>
            <p style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:2.5rem;color:var(--naranja);line-height:1;">5</p>
            <p style="font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">Obras originales</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:2.5rem;color:var(--naranja);line-height:1;">4</p>
            <p style="font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">Funciones en julio</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:2.5rem;color:var(--naranja);line-height:1;">11</p>
            <p style="font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">Integrantes en escena</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PIEZAS -->
<section id="piezas">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <span class="section-label">El programa</span>
    <h2 class="display section-title">Cinco piezas originales</h2>
    <div class="piezas-grid">
      <div class="pieza-card">
        <span class="pieza-num">I</span>
        <p class="pieza-titulo">Huga Buga</p>
        <p class="pieza-autor">por Emiliano Araiza</p>
        <p class="pieza-desc">Una tribu prehistórica, un hermano expulsado y la trampa de intentar ser alguien que no eres. Comedia física y absurdo cavernícola.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pieza-card">
        <span class="pieza-num">II</span>
        <p class="pieza-titulo">Amour Fou</p>
        <p class="pieza-autor">por Antónimo González, Karyme Soara y el Espíritu Santo</p>
        <p class="pieza-desc">El ciclo completo de una relación: fascinación, simbiosis, asfixia, ruptura. El humor funciona como anestesia: hace reír y de pronto duele.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pieza-card">
        <span class="pieza-num">III</span>
        <p class="pieza-titulo">Pan Invisible, Tiempo Inexistente</p>
        <p class="pieza-autor">por Yorlenny Espinosa</p>
        <p class="pieza-desc">Dos cocineros atrapados en una cocina sin ventanas. Un sándwich sin jamón. Un reloj roto. La pieza más tierna del programa.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pieza-card">
        <span class="pieza-num">IV</span>
        <p class="pieza-titulo">Los de Arriba</p>
        <p class="pieza-autor">por Freddy Páez</p>
        <p class="pieza-desc">Un director que recibe órdenes de eliminar a una actriz cuya espontaneidad incomoda al sistema. La bisagra donde el humor se oscurece.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pieza-card" style="background:#1a1816;">
        <span class="pieza-num" style="color:rgba(142,53,46,0.15);">V</span>
        <p class="pieza-titulo">La Quinta</p>
        <p class="pieza-autor">por Freddy Páez</p>
        <p class="pieza-desc">Todos los personajes convergen en un espacio sin salida. Los juicios comienzan. El cuarto muro cae. El público no sale ileso.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

